Dion Wired is re-opening its Fourways store, and the company is celebrating by offering discounts on a wide range of tech-related products. These deals are only available from 22-25 August at the company’s physical store in Fourways Mall. Limited quantities of products are available, and Dion Wired said only one discounted product per customer would be allowed. Devices on special include 4K smart TVs, flagship smartphones, JBL speaker systems, and high-end professional laptops. Below are some of the best deals available at Dion Wired’s Grand Re-Opening Sale at Fourways Mall. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317139" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Samsung-Galaxy-A30.jpg" alt="Samsung Galaxy A30" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Samsung-Galaxy-A30.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Samsung-Galaxy-A30-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Samsung-Galaxy-A30-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317137" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/LG-65-inch-UHD-Smart-TV.jpg" alt="LG 65-inch UHD Smart TV" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/LG-65-inch-UHD-Smart-TV.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/LG-65-inch-UHD-Smart-TV-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/LG-65-inch-UHD-Smart-TV-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317129" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/DStv-Explora.jpg" alt="DStv Explora" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/n